data.description: Charming home with many updates and plenty of space. Finished lower level offers extra living space. When you walk in you are greeted by a beautiful staircase that leads to a master suite area in the upper. The kitchen offers an eat in area along with a bar area for extra seating. Off the kitchen is a patio door and deck. The garage opens into the yard and the alley for extra parking and easy access. Large yard that can be turned into a beautiful outdoor space. Schedule a showing today!
